<div class="book bkPSA">
    <div class="chapter ch1" data-usfm="PSA.1">

        <div class="label">
        </div>

        <div class="s"> 
            <span class="heading">                          為善者昌                                                        </span> 
        </div>
        
        <div class="p">

            <span class="content">  
            </span>

            <span class="verse v1" data-usfm="PSA.1.1"> 
                <span class="label">                        1                                                               </span> 
                <span class="content">                      不從惡人之計謀、不登罪人之道途、不坐褻慢人之座位、             </span> 
            </span>

            <span class="verse v2" data-usfm="PSA.1.2"> 
                <span class="label">                        2                                                               </span> 
                <span class="content">                      惟喜悅主之律法、晝夜思維、似此之人、即為有福、                  </span> 
            </span>

            <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"> 
                <span class="label">                        3                                                               </span> 
                <span class="content">                      彼如樹木、植於溪旁、臨時結果、其葉不枯、所為之事、無不亨通、    </span> 
            </span>

        </div>

        <div class="s"> 
            <span class="heading">                          作惡者亡                                                        </span> 
        </div>

        <div class="p">

            <span class="verse v3" data-usfm="PSA.1.3"> 
                <span class="content">
                </span> 
            </span>

            <span class="verse v4" data-usfm="PSA.1.4"> 
                <span class="label">                        4                                                               </span> 
                <span class="content">                      維彼惡人、決不如此、乃如糠秕、隨風吹散、                        </span> 
            </span>

            <span class="verse v5" data-usfm="PSA.1.5"> 
                <span class="label">                        5                                                               </span>
                <span class="content">                      因此當審判時、惡人必不能立、罪人在善人會中、亦復若是、          </span> 
            </span>

            <span class="verse v6" data-usfm="PSA.1.6"> 
                <span class="label">                        6                                                               </span> 
                <span class="content">                      蓋主喜悅善人之道、惡人之道、必至滅亡、                          </span> 
            </span>

         </div>

    </div>
</div>
